  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단상자, 패키지, 박스 소량 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-40aad47f-c960-42e6-89fe-eb1b0968b567\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/000.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/001.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">소량 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">십자조립은 위 이미지처럼 조립되는 한 면만 접착된 박스입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-21bf6ee4-87e3-45dd-bef3-c77464d92b55\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39b3ce0e-0a82-4ae2-ae58-b24378f23907\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1a11b8f-4b72-44e8-9b27-206e7c21b311\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dcfc8e12-6230-498e-8cc0-21ece0ddff05\" style=\"color:#555555;\">십자조립은 하단을 양쪽으로 눌러서 앞쪽 면에 끼운 다음 다른 면 끼움새를 눌러서 조립합니다. 손쉽게 조립을 할 수 있고 한 면만 접착을 하기 때문에 삼면접착보다 가공비가 절약될 수 있으며 또한 하단을 깔끔하게 끼워질 수 있어서 양쪽 뚜껑형보다 더 밑면이 단단하고 견고하게 조립될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a50949d8-23c8-4c61-8995-d36f22b09186\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cd0dd8f8-901a-408b-b3a9-303023161e3a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b9769d70-09bf-40a2-8406-f3770e3c355c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6f7144af-d5d9-4968-8a82-eac8c11f3261\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f5908c7-e939-4958-bbe7-a7a764637d4d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하단의 전개도는 다음과 같은 형태로 구성되어 있습니다. 뚜껑형(엇뚜껑, 맞뚜껑)보다는 견고하게 조립할 수 있다는 강점이 있습니다. 다만 도면이 맞지 않으면 십자조립이 되지 않아서 불량이 발생할 수 있습니다. 반드시 사전에 도면을 확인하시고 발주하시기를 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1106d43a-4832-4966-a6fe-71aefb93364e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:667px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-11bb9685-5a5c-472e-b6bf-288d5bdc23f2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-69b4e3e4-c6b8-46d9-8fd6-1573a03224bb\" style=\"\">칼선이 맞지 않는 불량 도면</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c5adb14e-5969-4771-9e08-1fee030fd6b6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-87a4bed4-5a00-4dc2-9a2e-cf511c7f8987\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ecc78d1-7cc6-43bb-b594-a05534bf5573\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc3d71fa-4205-40f4-9ba8-dfc331881083\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3c58dcb9-e5a9-4939-b5f1-7ec6f6c2a1ec\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>십자조립에서 주의할 점</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6fdcc7e1-910a-45b1-85ec-21aa070089d2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n<a class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-694c11df-e9bc-454e-9760-eb9c0b8b529b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-09e12c3d-985a-4353-9419-0a65920a3419\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-89fa2362-f52a-4f65-8915-8d5f621d4ef6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>여기서 잠깐!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bc5c31f7-76a2-45d3-a485-4f7e13113b24\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b5a92641-0325-4810-a435-8bc549c1a22e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>└ 도면</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f2ced202-eaf8-4c04-a762-e2c5369f4095\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-18b4db45-8454-4102-a21b-2b8b8e3c94d5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">십자조립 제작 시 도면이 맞지 않게 되면 조립이 되지 않습니다. 뚜껑형들은 넓이만 맞으면 꺾어서 접어 들어갈 수 있지만 십자조립형은 끼워지는 부분이 너무 작게 전개도가 되어 있거나 양쪽 날개가 작아서 덮어지지 못하게 되는 경우가 발생될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20a68dcc-3245-449a-a427-2ebbc8900bbf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aca93e22-9b0a-4dc4-b189-5319ca07d26e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">반드시 도면은 확인하고 주문하세요. 저희도 몇 개월간 3건 이상의 도면 에러가 주문되어 사고가 발생했었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-9c5f4c40-a6ac-4bdd-9569-629ff4fb1ed5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c12be282-8e0b-474a-9956-677f721cc1b0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5f497b7e-983b-442b-8779-8bf5de27406f\" style=\"\">제작 일지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-86d9f353-3530-47eb-bd64-7300d5b7ab65\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:652px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-46473446-e3f9-4389-88aa-d087e9bec3b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5fe4edc-b8e3-4e1e-99a8-4ce0558c1670\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8ce9f879-5ed6-417b-962f-26f6324d0c2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">블로그를 보시고 급하게 주문해서 생산을 요청하는 내용이었습니다. 수요일 주문하여 토요일까지 생산을 요청하는 상황이라 저희 쪽의 생산 시설도 1차로 검증하고 답변을 드려야 하는 건이었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20f4519b-3371-4bb6-908a-8b6137e1170b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c298fde7-ad6b-4333-b501-642ec2f18649\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자사의 생산 상황과 고개님의 디자인 상태를 판단하고 납기 여부를 판단합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c11a36f8-c9ad-427c-b23b-d6e07d5af94d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e93b556-b3d0-4cac-90ae-effb913cb33c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87c6f9b5-f61b-46a0-b40c-d01b616327e7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:645px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-269ff7ce-9ded-44e8-8668-93b803e29a9f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-668924da-f071-48a7-bae4-dfd88042ad44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b0373c1f-c348-408b-8b82-9e2e1af72099\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량 주문을 원하시는 대표님은 항상 납기가 급한 건이 대부분이었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b84fb8dc-620a-4c11-b358-b848893e40dc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e964a3b7-a60c-4536-a820-27d8c536f885\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량 주문의 특징이 개당 단가는 비싸다고 할지라도 납기에 있어 분명히 강점이 있다 보니 수량 생산을 고민하여 주문하게 되십니다. 소량으로 주문하면 납기와 비용, 또는 보관비용 면에서 장점이 있습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-15edee60-185b-4a08-99a5-13b04725b6f0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-11ae6a70-4523-4132-80a6-96611e3f591f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-23e93b8c-fc68-49e1-9f66-59bd46ba6016\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:649px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b628df29-c5fa-4efe-908e-f4240bdde96a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ef364ef2-e597-4bf2-9b93-75eacb0c8f58\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c0922a7-a935-477a-ac18-91dae7cf2ac0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단가를 고려한 100개 주문이었습니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 항상 고객의 디자인을 체크하는 시스템을 가동합니다. 이 체크에서 많이 에러가 검증됩니다. 30년 경력의 디자이너가 여러 가지 측면을 고려한 데이터 검증 절차를 가지고 있습니다. 믿고 맡겨주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-24e9cdfc-0e22-4a67-afc6-3f35246fd3a3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c853e3b7-aacb-4cf9-8258-05926360da34\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-851c4d42-cb92-4374-ba51-bd0645077452\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bdd8e9da-d1d5-46f8-a332-30713806cfc7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이건이 바로 십자조립의 도면이 잘못된 불량 주문이었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-20594b1f-88ad-49a0-a46e-85a09e642b31\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:258px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2e4e5c7f-2c79-4a8d-86f4-06c12ae42b97\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8f442ed1-bb3f-40f3-bfa7-0a3ac91cfcbf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-81145281-4d8b-49e5-833e-ce2891c86b2b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기존 도면은 아래 그림처럼 전개도가 문제가 있어서 조립되지 않는 사고가 종종 발생합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-39c4fe89-736f-498f-96b4-39b50e6e4884\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0ab6cd2d-eb7b-4e01-86d6-c8920dacbd0c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e214f0c-94b0-4162-bff6-85a7e2cd4a7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4ce83d19-b129-4731-a6fb-fe7a835693e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">중국 쪽에서 넘어온 칼선이었다고 합니다. 칼선도 이미지로 되어 있었고 양면 날개도 너무 넓고 끼우는 부분의 간격도 맞지 않아 결국 조립이 불가능했었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c8e2286-d66e-4ace-90a9-a8750541464c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ec423a1d-e8ab-45f4-af1b-15946f81b500\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ab33f1d2-0dd2-429a-8e6d-08e6c638d332\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bdb09c91-811c-40bb-9087-8a42b9c3d32c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">결국은 재작업을 진행했습니다. 고객님의 상황을 고려하여 약간의 DC를 진행해 처리해 드렸습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-35514dc6-c537-48c0-83ac-28fe754b2746\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a028112-4c45-4bdd-a20b-3696b51e9eb3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-310c2ed3-85f2-4b4f-b73c-419347ce0109\" style=\"\">제작 사양</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80fbf998-7dd6-4f22-9e6b-3295578cc109\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a67029d-e01d-438c-b633-adede36f5070\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-dccd04d2-894e-469f-bf70-8ff253a40194\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>형태</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5bbe9ce8-e43c-4516-80c6-ecbde7f7e27b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 십자조립</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5919b362-1482-4ce5-82b4-15405671b860\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ea57cc62-be2e-47eb-a35a-0a2c6c36cfde\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7caf2df-9456-40be-8bbe-874ae98f9ddb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 인바이런먼트 352g 백색</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a13eebb-f271-442e-ab10-97a003f61380\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a8d7fce2-f985-4c20-af93-17c31c17b662\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1b3fe3e-372c-4484-b4d9-72444886ae0a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 65×55×185mm</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e96bf014-7f25-473b-b38d-30958fa1b499\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6024531a-858a-47fc-8b4f-f948c81eb3d8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ee0b7f94-c673-4d04-a92e-6ab6fb363281\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 단면 4도 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f82cab0-4c84-40f8-a020-584788620fc2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bb7875cf-8e9e-40fd-a6bd-a249825bb9d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f591a409-bd09-4d37-af69-7ee43ffa36c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 무광 코팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b610ec10-10b9-4e0d-a744-2d5d03d76a07\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-df79ffb8-c3f3-4286-92be-237e8f4266e4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-50e442b3-f8fb-4ca9-9211-4d1f8b7b0ab5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 디지털 커팅 + 접착</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-13269a07-406f-4b6d-876f-3d9a2bcf81ed\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b5e667d7-a4dd-4156-9a12-2ac19967c79b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa3eb311-fd77-4935-b460-0dd12ebb41b7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 100개</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af08d898-a74c-4524-9b73-36f0a620458f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-07dd78ba-4b41-4108-ae91-cceba7a1fe85\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단가</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b31463c2-d1d5-4214-9304-5f079abad592\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 비공개(별도문의)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-19fa2cbf-6c29-41ac-9833-ae17b5829c5d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-76829d42-a44f-49c4-90ca-5cf0f3778d93\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-46ed71a1-3122-4660-ae7a-189c28d7cece\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1c76c1a5-4ab6-4ffa-b647-c1ae0b89c6f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">결국은 도면 사고로 인해 재발주를 하고 진행하게 되었습니다. 이참에 디자인도 수정하고 칼선도 변경하여 제작하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-57496ca8-ad56-427f-b379-4cd5215a38df\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:646px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223915508485/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-15652307-b42a-458a-9732-e2a2fd73e3ca\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3019b94f-bf95-4caf-836f-a962b757ad7d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a4750af-919c-4a13-8fde-7cf41cd859b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주문 후 단 3일 안에 제작하여 발송해 드렸습니다. 택배가 하루 지연된 것을 제외하고는 전혀 문제가 발생하지 않았습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underl